deliver your closing argument.

528
00:37:41,780 --> 00:37:45,320
The defendant admits all of his actions...

529
00:37:45,450 --> 00:37:46,940
and is in deep remorse.

530
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:49,610
I hope you put that into consideration.

531
00:37:52,490 --> 00:37:55,930
Case number 2019G173.

532
00:37:56,130 --> 00:37:59,600
The defendant Park Su Myeong
is on trial for murder.

533
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:02,330
I will now deliver his sentence.

534
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:08,180
We sentence the defendant
to 20 years in prison.

535
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:10,760
No! You're wrong!

536
00:38:11,370 --> 00:38:12,900
My son didn't kill anyone!

537
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:15,570
My son isn't a monster!

538
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:18,310
- No!
- Don't hurt my mom.

539
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:21,220
- My boy... No!
- Not my mom!

540
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:23,370
- Get away from my mom.
- He's innocent!

541
00:38:23,520 --> 00:38:27,200
Mom, take me with you. I want to go home.

542
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:29,120
Mom, I want to go home!

543
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:32,870
- Mom!
- My boy!

544
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:35,230
- Mom!
- He's innocent!

545
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:39,380
Mom, I want to go home!

546
00:38:39,770 --> 00:38:42,630
My boy!

547
00:38:42,970 --> 00:38:44,330
Get away from my mom!

548
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,240
Mr. Kwon.

549
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,890
Please help my son.

550
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:16,310
He didn't kill anyone.

551
00:39:16,610 --> 00:39:19,370
I'm sorry about how I treated you before.

552
00:39:19,580 --> 00:39:22,210
You didn't know the truth, right?

553
00:39:22,580 --> 00:39:25,810
So please, help my boy.

554
00:39:28,950 --> 00:39:31,620
I understand what you're going through.

555
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,380
However, your son...

556
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:37,490
confessed his crimes in court.

557
00:39:37,490 --> 00:39:41,570
That's right. Then you
should've let him finish.

558
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:43,750
Why didn't you hear him out completely?

559
00:39:44,500 --> 00:39:48,580
My son only stabbed the victim once.

560
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:51,400
Then the second stab...

561
00:39:51,570 --> 00:39:53,760
