562
00:39:55,910 --> 00:39:58,640
He may be a lot of things, but my son...

563
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:00,900
never lies.

564
00:40:01,350 --> 00:40:04,150
I've been suspicious of
that Im Yun Hee woman.

565
00:40:06,860 --> 00:40:08,420
It seemed like she adored my son...

566
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:10,230
so much that she was willing
to go to jail for him,

567
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:13,160
but she hasn't visited him even once.

568
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:17,440
She disappeared from the neighborhood!

