594
00:42:26,100 --> 00:42:27,130
Cut. Okay!

595
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:29,710
Yun Seo, that was great.

596
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:34,100
My gosh.

597
00:42:35,690 --> 00:42:37,440
I'm sorry. Excuse me.

598
00:42:44,930 --> 00:42:47,520
I had no idea she could give deep emotions.

599
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:51,700
