absorbed in her character too.

600
00:42:52,230 --> 00:42:53,870
Her acting has improved a lot.

601
00:42:53,870 --> 00:42:56,600
She won't be called a
bad actor anymore now.

602
00:42:57,750 --> 00:43:01,250
Bad actor? You won't have to
worry about that ever again.

603
00:43:03,890 --> 00:43:05,330
- Director, please excuse me.
- Okay.

604
00:43:15,890 --> 00:43:17,180
Yun Seo, are you okay?

605
00:43:24,330 --> 00:43:25,820
Why are you crying?

606
00:43:27,910 --> 00:43:31,180
Is it because you were reminded of him?

607
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:32,690
I tried to forget...

608
00:43:35,270 --> 00:43:37,330
I tried so hard to forget about him.

609
00:43:39,310 --> 00:43:42,520
But whenever I think about
Mr. Kwon from time to time,

610
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:44,840
I become unbearably sad.

611
00:43:46,390 --> 00:43:50,220
I thought you were okay now.

612
00:43:50,230 --> 00:43:53,470
How could I be okay? I liked him so much.

613
00:43:58,060 --> 00:44:00,120
But there's nothing I can do.

614
00:44:00,680 --> 00:44:01,990
I must think of my fans...

615
00:44:02,480 --> 00:44:05,170
and everyone who is
waiting for my comeback.

616
00:44:10,080 --> 00:44:12,270
