618
00:44:20,830 --> 00:44:22,240
I'm sorry, Hyuk Joon.

619
00:44:23,790 --> 00:44:24,980
I'll try my best...

620
00:44:26,870 --> 00:44:28,280
to control my feelings.

621
00:44:28,730 --> 00:44:29,950
Don't worry.

622
00:44:31,940 --> 00:44:34,460
Okay. I'm sorry too.

623
00:44:34,870 --> 00:44:36,390
You should get some rest, Yun Seo.

624
00:44:46,790 --> 00:44:48,530
I wonder if he's doing well.

625
00:44:51,020 --> 00:44:53,120
During Im Yun Hee's first hearing,

626
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:55,720
Park Su Myeong was pointed
out as the real culprit,

627
00:44:55,850 --> 00:44:57,610
and she was released on bail.

628
00:44:57,770 --> 00:44:59,790
After that, her whereabouts remain unknown.

629
