There were a total of 11 insurances
signed under Kim Yeong Tae's name.

632
00:45:12,270 --> 00:45:15,200
A part of the insurance
payouts went to Im Yun Hee.

633
00:45:15,480 --> 00:45:18,110
Out of a total 4.49 million
dollars for his death benefit,

634
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:19,630
2.73 million was paid to her.

635
00:45:21,350 --> 00:45:23,120
Was that insurance payout...

636
00:45:23,120 --> 00:45:25,980
She withdrew all of it
in cash and disappeared.

637
00:45:27,750 --> 00:45:31,400
She disappeared when the insurance
payout wasn't fully paid.

638
00:45:31,560 --> 00:45:32,880
Something seems fishy, right?

639
00:45:33,020 --> 00:45:36,070
First, let's go meet the employee
at the insurance company.

640
00:45:37,910 --> 00:45:40,100
When did you first meet Ms. Im Yun Hee?

641
00:45:40,100 --> 00:45:41,590
February 27.

642
00:45:42,480 --> 00:45:45,880
She had to sign some papers
regarding the insurance payout,

643
00:45:46,040 --> 00:45:47,190
so we met briefly.

644
00:45:48,370 --> 00:45:49,800
We met at this cafe.

645
00:45:50,020 --> 00:45:52,610
Do you remember anything
particular from your conversation?

646
00:45:52,790 --> 00:45:55,380
For instance, did she say
where she was going...

647
00:45:55,410 --> 00:45:56,970
or whom she was planning to meet?

648
00:45:58,060 --> 00:46:00,480
No. There was nothing special
about our conversation.

649
00:46:03,960 --> 00:46:04,970
But...

650
00:46:05,620 --> 00:46:08,630
