Right. I got overexcited.

704
00:49:30,230 --> 00:49:31,880
I was a bit out of line there.

705
00:49:33,140 --> 00:49:36,100
Right. I'm not in a situation
to go there right now.

706
00:49:37,080 --> 00:49:38,220
Of course not.

707
00:49:43,480 --> 00:49:47,280
I thought we were going for lunch.
Why are we at court?

708
00:49:47,290 --> 00:49:49,540
Why? I'm thinking of having lunch...

709
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:52,810
at the cafeteria that's
located inside this court.

