The cafeteria at this place is
really famous for its food.

711
00:49:56,460 --> 00:49:59,190
What? I've never heard anything like that.

712
00:49:59,660 --> 00:50:01,350
I'm glad you heard it now.

713
00:50:02,790 --> 00:50:05,560
The reason why I won all
those numerous trials...

714
00:50:05,600 --> 00:50:08,260
is because of the delicious
food from the cafeteria here.

715
00:50:08,330 --> 00:50:10,830
I received good energy
and became successful.

716
00:50:13,100 --> 00:50:16,650
Mr. Yeon. Did you come here to
look at the drama shooting?

717
00:50:16,980 --> 00:50:18,960
Yes... No.

718
00:50:19,080 --> 00:50:20,910
Is that a yes or no?

719
00:50:20,910 --> 00:50:22,300
Yes, no. No.

720
00:50:23,350 --> 00:50:26,050
I mean, I didn't actually
come to see the filming site.

721
00:50:26,060 --> 00:50:28,890
