a bad idea to take a look around.

722
00:50:28,890 --> 00:50:30,480
Don't take it the wrong way.

723
00:50:30,600 --> 00:50:34,470
She used to be our staff,
and pretending not to know is rude.

724
00:50:36,440 --> 00:50:39,230
And didn't you two say
you missed Ms. Oh last time?

725
00:50:39,270 --> 00:50:40,320
You did, right?

726
00:50:40,480 --> 00:50:42,520
To boost the energy of my employees,

727
00:50:42,580 --> 00:50:44,930
I've decided to sacrifice myself...

728
00:50:44,980 --> 00:50:46,440
and come take a stroll near here.

729
00:50:46,440 --> 00:50:48,900
But where is Ms. Oh?

730
00:50:49,140 --> 00:50:51,580
I'm sorry, but you can't come near.

731
00:50:51,580 --> 00:50:54,380
- Okay.
- You might be caught on camera.

732
00:50:54,750 --> 00:50:57,150
