is not well acquainted...

737
00:51:10,870 --> 00:51:12,250
with the famous Ms. Oh Yun Seo?

738
00:51:12,730 --> 00:51:15,560
We'll begin shooting soon,
so we'd appreciate your cooperation.

739
00:51:16,040 --> 00:51:17,490
Let's just go, Mr. Yeon.

740
00:51:17,850 --> 00:51:20,170
- Ms. Yang.
- Yes, you can begin shooting.

741
00:51:20,180 --> 00:51:22,870
Do I really have to mention
the fact that I am...

742
00:51:22,870 --> 00:51:25,510
