744
00:51:28,890 --> 00:51:30,450
He must be so flustered.

745
00:51:30,460 --> 00:51:32,050
No, I mean...

746
00:51:32,060 --> 00:51:34,480
It's all right, stop mentioning it.

747
00:51:35,390 --> 00:51:38,500
I didn't know, but you are
really bad at keeping secrets.

748
00:51:38,960 --> 00:51:41,730
Why don't you just tell him that I
was also on national television...

749
00:51:41,730 --> 00:51:44,360
for a debate show and
also numerous TV programs,

750
00:51:44,370 --> 00:51:46,930
and that I'm a famous
attorney while you're at it?

751
00:51:48,640 --> 00:51:51,140
Why don't you just
outright tell him that...

752
00:51:51,140 --> 00:51:54,910
the law firm Oh Yun Seo used
to work at was our law firm?

753
00:51:58,410 --> 00:51:59,630
Mr. Yeon.

754
00:52:03,980 --> 00:52:05,240
Ms. Oh.

755
00:52:06,080 --> 00:52:07,940
Ms. Oh is running towards me.

756
00:52:08,850 --> 00:52:10,340
She's even calling my name.

757
00:52:13,790 --> 00:52:15,850
Ms. Yang, Hae Yeong.

758
00:52:17,270 --> 00:52:18,320
How did you come here?

759
00:52:19,310 --> 00:52:22,300
I really missed you.
It's so nice to see you.

760
00:52:22,310 --> 00:52:23,390
Me too.

761
00:52:24,350 --> 00:52:27,200
What brings the three of you here?

