854
00:58:25,310 --> 00:58:27,970
Like I already told you,
that's something I should deal with...

855
00:58:27,980 --> 00:58:30,330
Then what about our firm?
What about the people who work here?

856
00:58:30,940 --> 00:58:33,030
Do you not care that our reputation
might get ruined because of you?

857
00:58:33,500 --> 00:58:34,730
If you have the least amount...

858
00:58:35,080 --> 00:58:37,810
of affection and sense of
duty for this law firm,

859
00:58:38,350 --> 00:58:39,600
