860
00:58:41,250 --> 00:58:42,500
You really can't do this to me.

861
00:59:04,540 --> 00:59:08,280
Hey, I heard you filed a POA
for the Park Su Myeong case.

862
00:59:08,620 --> 00:59:09,690
What happened?

863
00:59:10,310 --> 00:59:12,840
- It just happened.
- My gosh, seriously.

864
00:59:13,210 --> 00:59:15,030
You'll have to put a lot at risk.

865
00:59:15,890 --> 00:59:17,400
Is that really necessary?

866
00:59:37,640 --> 00:59:39,160
To be honest, I'm scared.

867
00:59:41,750 --> 00:59:43,730
I don't know what the truth is yet.

868
00:59:44,750 --> 00:59:46,230
But my rash decision...

869
00:59:47,520 --> 00:59:49,740
could've driven someone to
the point of no return.

870
00:59:53,430 --> 00:59:54,570
And the fact that I could end up...

871
00:59:57,370 --> 01:00:00,090
leaving a scar on someone that
they won't be able to forget...

872
01:00:00,600 --> 01:00:02,250
for the rest of their lives...

873
01:00:09,870 --> 01:00:11,020
really scares me.

874
01:00:12,370 --> 01:00:16,210
But if I turn away from this...

875
01:00:18,890 --> 01:00:21,310
and lose my chance to set things straight,

876
01:00:26,350 --> 01:00:29,420
not only will I lose the right
to be anyone's attorney,

877
01:00:31,790 --> 01:00:34,520
but I'll also lose my confidence
to defend anyone at all.

878
