defending Park Su Myeong?

889
01:01:52,940 --> 01:01:54,560
Yes, that's what I heard.

890
01:01:55,810 --> 01:01:56,930
My gosh.

891
01:01:58,040 --> 01:02:01,320
He's the one who pointed
him out as the culprit.

892
01:02:01,910 --> 01:02:03,700
And now, he wishes to defend him?

893
01:02:08,690 --> 01:02:10,370
Is he joking right now?

894
01:02:18,210 --> 01:02:20,560
Hello, sir. I'm Koo Sung Gil
from Daehan Daily.

895
01:02:21,580 --> 01:02:22,970
I heard Park Su Myeong and his attorney...

896
01:02:22,980 --> 01:02:24,490
