897
01:02:24,870 --> 01:02:25,880
Is that true?

898
01:02:27,410 --> 01:02:28,630
I'm not sure.

899
01:02:28,810 --> 01:02:30,760
But even if that happens,
I don't think anything will change.

900
01:02:36,520 --> 01:02:38,580
I actually heard some interesting news.

901
01:02:42,430 --> 01:02:44,450
- Mr. Kwon.
- He's here.

902
01:02:44,460 --> 01:02:46,320
