912
01:03:05,080 --> 01:03:06,160
What are your thoughts on this case?

913
01:03:06,480 --> 01:03:08,580
According to the Attorneys' Code of Ethics,

914
01:03:08,960 --> 01:03:12,590
when a conflict of interest
arises between two clients,

915
01:03:12,850 --> 01:03:14,470
